# Mobile-First UX

## Targets

- Log meal: **&lt;10s** from tap-+ to saved
- Log weight: **&lt;5s**
- FCP &lt;1.5s on 4G

## Today view

- Default route shows **today** (Asia/Jerusalem)
- Day nav: **swipe** on mobile, **arrow buttons** on desktop
- Four slots, **multiple entries** per slot
- Progress bar: consumed / target, remaining kcal

## Meal entry

1. Optimistic row immediately (`...` calories)
2. Spinner until estimate or cache returns
3. On failure: retry + manual calorie override (FR-13, FR-14)

## Weight

- Bottom sheet: kg input (1 decimal), date default today
- Graph: Recharts line; default range 90d; tap point for value
- List: tap edit, swipe delete

## Navigation

- Fixed bottom nav: **Today | Weight | Settings**

## Could (don't block v1)

- PWA manifest, 7-day calorie average footer, graph range toggles beyond 90d default
